{"tid":1495036,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有報導指長實要求酒店員工放無薪假","createTime":"2019-08-22T01:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T13:49:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5ffc9693b453a1850626360d6c49caab414a2e","tid":1495036,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰加速亞太區內以至全球經濟放緩，加上反修例運動早前阻礙航空交通令訪港旅客卻步，<span style=\"color: red;\">有報導指長實集團（01113）旗下酒店要求全體員工，本月起放無薪假</span>。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》報導指，<span style=\"color: red;\">長實旗下10間酒店昨日發出口頭通知，要求全體員工本月起放無薪假</span>。其中酒店主管級員工於8月餘下時間放1天無薪假，9月份則放2天、基層員工則需放1天。長實方面暫未置評。<br />\n<br />\n深入反修例爭議風眼的國泰航空（00293）昨日公布的7月客貨運量數據，顯示7月客運量雖仍有約4%增長，惟各地區中，<span style=\"color: red;\">內地客量已率先下跌2.8%</span>。國泰並預告，「8月及往後的收益將顯著受壓」。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊界立法會議員姚思榮早前向本網表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">擔心若示威持續，訪港旅客量跌幅可能擴至4至5成， 並不知道何時能反彈</span>。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》引述長實本月初公布的中期業績，上半年酒店及服務套房業務收入為23.74億元，按年下跌2.1%；扣除物業折舊1.97億元後的收益則為8.76億元，按年微升0.7%；期內平均入住率為89.5%。<br />\n<br />\n長實現時在本港共經運10間酒店，包括都會海逸酒店、北角海逸酒店、嘉湖海逸酒店、8度海逸酒店、九龍海灣酒店、九龍酒店、港島海逸君綽酒店、九龍海逸君綽酒店、華逸酒店及青逸酒店。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2432856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2432856%2F&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIX9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=2c2ad4a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2432856/</a>"},{"pid":"8600557d1dc7cb192612793b143685fb3055f117","tid":1495036,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"已經有人停薪留職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c20847616567bdf31256ee11fce7fe86a203dba","tid":1495036,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"變相罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03789ad5459767f96213c71f0845a9a2c838f106","tid":1495036,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:48:06.000Z","msg":"有賺就唔講, 蝕少少就即刻劏鳩d員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf3e9301fc3daf5038a56f186dd2dbfe16ace61","tid":1495036,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"037489c1daae60efc983e257ff04e4310a0f6c88","tid":1495036,"uid":83172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fake news<br />\n利申 旗下酒店員工"},{"pid":"39e777eb39674345b35afc2f16c8805df3da821c","tid":1495036,"uid":144447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T02:26:01.000Z","msg":"玩藏頭詩,我就唱衰你"},{"pid":"aa89a3d9944da70cad343bc4484ac9a62f2ac431","tid":1495036,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"037489c1daae60efc983e257ff04e4310a0f6c88","tid":1495036,"uid":83172,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fake news<br />\n利申 旗下酒店員工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"但長實無出來澄清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}